org.paukov.combinatorics - package org.paukov.combinatorics
This package contains common classes and interfaces of the library such as ICombinatoricsVector, Generator and Factory.
org.paukov.combinatorics.combination.multi - package org.paukov.combinatorics.combination.multi
This package contains the multicombinations generator (combinations with repetitions).
org.paukov.combinatorics.combination.simple - package org.paukov.combinatorics.combination.simple
This package contains the simple combinations generator.
org.paukov.combinatorics.composition - package org.paukov.combinatorics.composition
This package contains the integer composition generators.
org.paukov.combinatorics.partition - package org.paukov.combinatorics.partition
This package contains the integer partitions generator.
org.paukov.combinatorics.permutations - package org.paukov.combinatorics.permutations
This package contains the generators for the permutations with and without repetitions.
org.paukov.combinatorics.subsets - package org.paukov.combinatorics.subsets
This package contains the subsets generators.
org.paukov.combinatorics.util - package org.paukov.combinatorics.util
This package contains the utility classes and tools.
org.paukov.tool - package org.paukov.tool
This package contains various tools.
